        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Drills, mechanics, and breakdowns filmed up close — no fluff, no filler.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-7 border border-gray-100">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
